data.description: OPEN HOUSE 7.18 NOON TO 4.  Imagine yourself in a stunning Glengarry Cape Cod with a 3 Car Side entry garage in a Cul De Sac, perfect for children! This 4 Bedroom 3.5 bath with a finished basement is a family’s dream.  Bentley elementary school is within walking distance. The first floor Master Bedroom and living room feature vaulted ceilings. The updated master bath has a double Jacuzzi tub, separate walk-in shower, and 2 walk in closets.  Windows, doors, roof,  and furnace have all been updated.  Lots of big windows with Hunter Douglas treatments. Open floor plan with great light and good flow throughout. The large kitchen with island is great for entertaining.  Make this home your own!!!
